<h3>{% trans %}Extending with new adapters{% endtrans %}</h3>
<ol>
  <li>{% trans %}Create a service implementing KnowledgeAdapterInterface and tag it with <code>bm_knowledge_ai.adapter</code>.{% endtrans %}</li>
  <li>{% trans %}Return KnowledgeItems from <code>normalize()</code> with stable IDs and source types (e.g., <code>node</code>, <code>document</code>).{% endtrans %}</li>
  <li>{% trans %}Optionally map taxonomy terms via configuration to enable filtering and explainability.{% endtrans %}</li>
</ol>
